Interface Slotable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BackboneSlotNode, SlotNode

    public interface Slotable
extends javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode
    This interface is intended to allow tree nodes that represent 'styles' that can be placed in slots to interface appropriately.
    Author:
    Eric Marinier
